# PC-4: Performance Budget
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Performance-sensitive features

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Performance Budget: Acceptable limits for response times, memory, or throughput.

ENFORCE: All features must operate within defined time, memory, and throughput thresholds.
PROHIBIT: Exceeding performance budgets without approval.
ON VIOLATION: Escalate to Performance Engineering Skill; provide optimization recommendations.
